title: Dataframes, Collections, and Streams in Java
description:
Wanna go full Data Scientist or Collection Ninja* with Java? We've got your back!


Join us on our fun adventure of exploring the world of dataframes, collections, and streams!


We will be using built-in features in Java, as well as libraries like Eclipse Collections and Dataframe-EC.


--------

*) Collection Ninja - someone who knows how to manipulate collections like wielding a samurai sword
